definitions.definition: An antelope of either of the genera Gazella (mostly native to Africa ), Procapra (native to Asia ), Eudorcas , or Nanger , capable of running at high speeds for long periods.

main_definition: An antelope of either of the genera Gazella (mostly native to Africa ), Procapra (native to Asia ), Eudorcas , or Nanger , capable of running at high speeds for long periods.
